 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf55e5e0778ba9ea57b576672620c07d58a11857","tid":1542290,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88258f40e9496a889d07374110482ffb49aef700","tid":1542290,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b919a36fc2018fcbb5f5ed738e14c83a8dd155cb","tid":1542290,"uid":12609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3a506e4b797711d48f384cfcb9dfe3abe4b2ea86","tid":1542290,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T20:58:58.000Z","msg":"美國當局本月1日調高價值1,100億美元（下同‧約8,583億港元）中國商品的關稅稅率，稅率增至15%，中國無人機品牌大疆（DJI）在新關稅實施後，調高旗下的無人機的價格，增幅15%，相當於將新增的關稅全部轉給消費者。<br />\n<br />\n美國科技網站The Verge發現，DJI旗下的產品全線加價，其中售價最便宜的Mavic Air Arctic White，售價從799元（約6,232港元）增至919元（約7,168港元），加幅15%；Mavic 2 Pro售價則由1,499元（約1.16萬港元）增至1,729元（約1.34萬港元）；而售價最貴的Mavic 2 Pro &amp; DJI Goggles RE，亦從1,948元（約1.51萬港元）增至2,178元（約1.69萬港元），加幅11.8%。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，在美國未加徵關稅之前，當地的售價與加拿大、法國、德國的價格都是一致的，而在宣佈加價後，民眾到加拿大購買Mavic 2 Pro，折合美元的售價仍是1,499美元。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述DJI的發言人稱，由於關稅增加，所以調高美國產品的售價，但強調在不同國家的定價時考慮很多不同因素，包括關稅、稅率和貨幣匯率波動等等。不過，報道指這是中國生產的品牌，首次將特朗普關稅成本，轉嫁給美國消費者的事例。<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60008824\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60008824&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=56bd22f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D60008824&h=3b460f4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=60008824</a><br />\n<br />\n成本加15%--&gt;所以要售價加15%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T21:02:46.0